# OrganAIzedCrime

A CLI for querying MITRE ATLAS: The adversarial threat matrix for AI/ML systems.

Built as the bedrock layer of a larger AI/ML offensive security learning platform.

## Setup

    git clone https://github.com/jennshaggy/-organAIzedcrime.git
    cd -organAIzedcrime
    go build -o atlas .
    ./atlas fetch

## Commands

    atlas fetch                        Download latest ATLAS data from GitHub
    atlas tactics list                 List all tactics
    atlas tactic get <name>            Get a tactic and its techniques
    atlas technique get <id>           Get a technique by ATLAS ID (e.g. AML.T0000)

## Example

    $ atlas tactic get reconnaissance

    === Reconnaissance ===
    The adversary is trying to gather information...

    --- Techniques ---
      [AML.T0000] Search Open Technical Databases
      [AML.T0002] Search Victim-Owned Websites

## Built with

- [Go](https://golang.org)
- [Cobra](https://github.com/spf13/cobra)
- [MITRE ATLAS](https://atlas.mitre.org)